uld be made to more mechanism/location specific terms.\n119898-property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31143\" xsd:anyURI\n119899:is_obsolete: true\n119900-\n119901-[Term]\n--\n119905-def: \"OBSOLETE. The directed movement of norepinephrine into, out of or within a cell, or between cells, by means of some agent such as a transporter or pore. Norepinephrine (3,4-dihydroxyphenyl-2-aminoethanol) is a hormone secreted by the adrenal medulla and a neurotransmitter in the sympathetic peripheral nervous system and in some tracts of the CNS. It is also the biosynthetic precursor of epinephrine.\" [GOC:ai, ISBN:0198506732]\n119906:comment: The reason for obsoletion is that this is an unnecessary grouping term and annotations should be made to more mechanism/location specific terms.\n119907-property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31143\" xsd:anyURI\n119908:is_obsolete: true\n119909-\n119910-[Term]\n--\n119916-synonym: \"vitamin or cofactor transport\" EXACT []\n119917:is_obsolete: true\n119918-consider: GO:0051180\n119919-\n--\n120092-property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/21394\" xsd:anyURI\n120093:is_obsolete: true\n120094-\n120095-[Term]\n--\n120109-property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/21394\" xsd:anyURI\n120110:is_obsolete: true\n120111-\n120112-[Term]\n--\n120118-property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/27153\" xsd:anyURI\n120119:is_obsolete: true\n120120-\n120121-[Term]\n--\n120127-property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/21394\" xsd:anyURI\n120128:is_obsolete: true\n120129-\n120130-[Term]\n--\n120144-property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/21394\" xsd:anyURI\n120145:is_obsolete: true\n120146-\n120147-[Term]\n--\n120162-property_value: term_trac